headline: Maxim Reserves GE Vernova Turbine To Fuel Alberta's Energy Future
summary: Maxim Powe signs a reservation agreement with GE Vernova for a 7HA.02 gas turbine, advancing 400 MW Prairie Lights Power project in Alberta.
